{"title":"Diarrea Crónica","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología/- Diarrea Crónica-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Diarrea\\Ncrónica","guid":"ZGbzwneJ0WwE5oxKTKjmNw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Causas","guid":"Nx_2_wSFAm9p4C_jG4bqwQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Según frecuencia","guid":"cjXVvWRNBfcbCVpZMNfKVA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Frecuentes","guid":"B9nuYhwoZ_EeswlYChBT6Q","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"1. Síndrome de\\NIntestino Irritable (SII)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Diagnóstico: Criterios de Roma IV, examen físico normal, análisis de sangre\\Ny deposiciones normales (calprotectina normal).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"2. Diarrea por\\NÁcidos Biliares (AB)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Diagnóstico: Estudios de malaabsorción de AB (no disponibles rutinariamente). Terapia empírica con colestiramina.","guid":"K802TEY9qO1SGSzbEGg0Hg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Pruebas: Medición de AB en deposiciones de 24 h, test respiratorio con glicocolato marcado con 14C, Se75HCAT.","guid":"F6rwtE4E6coLWRC5TpU_sg","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"3","text":"3. Dieta","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Causas: Malabsorción de FODMAP, lactosa, consumo excesivo de cafeína, alcohol, sorbitol, goma de mascar.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"3","text":"4. Cáncer Colorrectal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Síntomas: Cambio de hábito intestinal, diarrea, anemia (posible ausencia de rectorragia). Diagnóstico: Colonoscopía.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"3","text":"5. Enfermedad Inflamatoria\\NIntestinal (EII)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Enfermedad de Crohn: Diarrea intermitente, compromiso nutricional.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Colitis Ulcerosa: Diarrea disentérica, pujo, tenesmo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• Diagnóstico: Colonoscopía y biopsias.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"3","text":"6. Enfermedad Celíaca","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Diagnóstico: Medición de anticuerpos (anticuerpos antitransglutaminasa, IgA). Confirmación: Biopsias duodenales.","guid":"UdsOOj3ZgvJj4bm3Z3CIHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"3","text":"7. Colitis Microscópica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Tipos: Colitis colagenosa, colitis linfocítica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Diagnóstico: Colonoscopía y biopsias escalonadas. Tratamiento: Budesonida.","guid":"UDWt0maQQfRQ0W5lNBRibA","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"3","text":"8. Fármacos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Causas: Antibióticos (macrólidos), AINEs, magnesio, hipoglicemiantes orales,\\Nantineoplásicos, antidepresivos, IECA, metformina, furosemida.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"2","text":"Infrecuentes","guid":"KdUmsXs0C24lE0eFdWaw7A","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"1. Sobrecrecimiento Bacteriano en\\NIntestino Delgado (SIBO)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Diagnóstico: Test de aire espirado con glucosa o lactulosa.\\NTratamiento: Rifaximina, eritromicina.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"2. Isquemia Mesentérica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Diagnóstico: Imagen contrastada abdominal (especialmente en pacientes mayores con antecedentes cardiovasculares).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"3. Insuficiencia\\NPancreática","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Diagnóstico: Esteatorrea (> 7 g/día de grasa en heces con dieta de 100 g de grasa/día).\\NTratamiento: Enzimas pancreáticas orales.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"2","text":"Raras","guid":"JHiKvj9LrLMy-CU3TxzO5A","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"1. Diarrea Facticia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Mecanismo: Uso subrepticio de laxantes, adulteración de muestras de heces.","guid":"PqH0l3cxiSEeua_qRnvi-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"2. Tumores\\NNeuroendocrinos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Diagnóstico: Medición de hormonas/péptidos en sangre u orina, gammagrafía con octreótido marcado (Octreoscan) o PET-DOTATE.\\NTratamiento: Resolución quirúrgica según tamaño de la lesión.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"3. Otras Causas Raras","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• Enteropatías (Enfermedad de Whipple, amiloidosis), Enfermedad de Addison, hipoparatiroidismo.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"1","text":"Según\\Nmecanismo","guid":"LRAUkRVUof5CeiIfPykdtA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Diarrea\\NAcuosa","guid":"W36PGDnDCkN3U61NbtiAKw","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Osmótica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Mecanismo: ↑sustancias no absorbidas en lumen intestinal → agua al lumen.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Exógenas: Laxantes osmóticos (Mg2+, lactulosa), antiácidos (Mg2+), sorbitol.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Endógenas: Enfermedades malabsortivas (celiaquía, insuficiencia pancreática), intolerancia a lactosa/fructosa.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"39","text":"• Características:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Cede con ayuno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"• Anion gap aumentado, pH ácido (<6).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"39","text":"• Secretora:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Mecanismo: Estímulo secretor → ↑AMPc en enterocito → apertura canales Cl- → agua al lumen.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"39","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Infecciosas: Enterotoxinas bacterianas (V. cholerae).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Endocrinas: VIPoma, carcinoide, glucagonoma.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"• Medicamentos: Prostaglandinas, ácidos biliares.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"39","text":"• Características:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• No cede con ayuno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"• Anion gap normal, pH neutro (>6).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"• Deshidratación frecuente.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"38","text":"Diarrea Esteatorreica\\N(Malabsortiva)","guid":"dy_DhUff5DAZ3WHyAqFmkg","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Malabsorción\\NIntestinal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• Inflamatorias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Enfermedad celíaca (anticuerpos, biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Enfermedad de Crohn (TAC, endoscopía, biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Enteritis actínica (historia, endoscopía).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"• Enteritis eosinofílica (biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"59","text":"• Infecciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Giardia lamblia, Cryptosporidium.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Mycobacterium (TBC, avium).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"• Tropheryma whipplei (Enf. de Whipple).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"59","text":"• Infiltrativas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Amiloidosis, esclerodermia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Linfoma (perdedora de proteínas).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"59","text":"• Anatómica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• Resección intestinal, by-pass.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"58","text":"• Maldigestión\\NPancreática:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• Etiologías:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• Pancreatitis crónica (TAC, grasa fecal, elastasa-1 fecal).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"• Fibrosis quística.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"• Tumor pancreático.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"74","text":"• Test: Sudán III fecal.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"38","text":"Diarrea\\NDisentérica","guid":"I8UrzRN3g2s54D_rRegcVg","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Enfermedad Inflamatoria\\NIntestinal (EII):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Colitis Ulcerosa:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Diagnóstico: Colonoscopía, biopsia.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"• Enfermedad de Crohn:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Diagnóstico: TAC, colonoscopía, biopsia.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"• Colitis Isquémica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"• Diagnóstico: Angiografía mesentérica, colonoscopía, biopsia.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"80","text":"• Colitis Actínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• Diagnóstico: Historia clínica, colonoscopía.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"38","text":"Diarrea por\\NMecanismos\\NCombinados","guid":"XyrRwAGHTWM55hsaaLejBg","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• Sobrecrecimiento\\NBacteriano (SIBO):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Mecanismo: ↑bacterias en intestino delgado → malabsorción, secreción.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"• Estasis intestinal (divertículos, estenosis).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"• Alteraciones de la motilidad (esclerodermia, diabetes).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"90","text":"• Desconjugación de\\NSales Biliares:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Mecanismo: Alteración en absorción de grasas → esteatorrea, secreción.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Enfermedades hepáticas, resección ileal.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"90","text":"• Fermentación de\\NCarbohidratos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Mecanismo: ↑carbohidratos no absorbidos → fermentación bacteriana → ↑ácidos grasos de cadena corta.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• Intolerancia a lactosa, SIBO.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"1","text":"Según\\NLocalización","guid":"QZSXRlBRA6R7F02IaQiX_Q","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"• Diarrea del\\NIntestino Delgado:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Volumen: Alto.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• Frecuencia: Menor (2-3 veces/día).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"• Consistencia: Acuosa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"• Presencia de sangre: Rara.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"105","text":"• Presencia de grasa: Posible.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"105","text":"• Dolor abdominal: Generalizado o periumbilical.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"105","text":"• Urgencia defecatoria: Menor.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"105","text":"• Síntomas asociados: Deshidratación, pérdida de peso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"105","text":"• Causas comunes: Infecciones, malabsorción.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"104","text":"• Diarrea del\\NIntestino Grueso:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Volumen: Bajo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"• Frecuencia: Mayor (>4 veces/día).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"• Consistencia: Pastosa, con moco.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"115","text":"• Presencia de sangre: Común.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"115","text":"• Presencia de grasa: No.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"115","text":"• Dolor abdominal: Localizado en parte baja.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"115","text":"• Urgencia defecatoria: Alta.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"115","text":"• Síntomas asociados: Fiebre, compromiso general.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"115","text":"• Causas comunes: Colitis infecciosa, EII.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación\\NClínica","guid":"JPic3wiDpn5X7wQGTxYoUw","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Funcional:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Intermitente, períodos de diarrea y deposiciones normales/estreñimiento.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"• Acuosa, sin sangre (puede tener mucus), solo diurna.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"• No asociada a baja de peso u otros signos de alarma.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"• Orgánica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"• Duración de meses, predominio nocturno, continua, con baja de peso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"• Puede incluir colitis microscópica, enfermedad de Crohn.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"125","text":"• Tipos de Diarrea\\NOrgánica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• Inflamatoria.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"• Malabsorción (esteatorrea).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"• Acuosa.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación\\NClínica","guid":"EPkdAHK-dC1AUNyiBmmqvg","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"Anamnesis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Comienzo y\\Nevolución temporal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Duración >4 semanas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"• Carácter episódico o continuo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"• Características de\\Nlas deposiciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• Frecuencia, volumen, consistencia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"• Presencia de sangre/moco.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"138","text":"• Síntomas\\Nasociados:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• Dolor abdominal, fiebre, pérdida de peso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"• Síntomas extraintestinales (artralgias, erupciones cutáneas).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"138","text":"• Historia médica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"• Enfermedades crónicas (VIH, diabetes, endocrinopatías).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"• Cirugías previas (resección intestinal).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"• Medicamentos (laxantes, antibióticos).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"138","text":"• Factores de riesgo: Viajes, exposición a tóxicos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"137","text":"Examen Físico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Estado nutritivo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"• IMC, pérdida de peso reciente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"• Signos de malnutrición (caquexia, hiperpigmentación cutánea).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"• Examen abdominal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• Dolor a la palpación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"• Masa palpable.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"• Hepatomegalia, esplenomegalia.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"153","text":"• Otros signos clínicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"• Bocio, lesiones cutáneas, linfadenopatías.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"137","text":"Diarrea Crónica\\NFuncional (SII)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"• Criterios de Roma IV:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"• Dolor abdominal recurrente (al menos 1 día/sem en últimos 3 meses).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"• Relacionado con defecación, cambio en frecuencia/forma de las heces.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"163","text":"• Ausencia de\\Nsignos de alarma:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Edad >50 años, sangrado digestivo, dolor nocturno, fiebre.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"• Pérdida de peso, alteraciones del examen físico.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"163","text":"• Exámenes\\Nrecomendados:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"• Hemograma, VHS.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"• Perfil bioquímico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"• Ac. antitransglutaminasa (en casos sospechosos).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"170","text":"• Calprotectina fecal (en caso de duda diagnóstica).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico\\NDiferencial","guid":"J3QAtjLqKQoxVODAS-yLdA","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"Datos Clínicos\\NRelevantes:","guid":"AjZlh3uCiMMvUeByAUi80A","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"1. Historia familiar: EII, neoplasias, enfermedad celíaca.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"2. Antecedentes de cirugías: Resecciones ileales/ileocecales (sobrecrecimiento bacteriano, malabsorción, diarrea por ácidos biliares). 10% post-colecistectomía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"3. Enfermedad pancreática previa: Pancreatitis crónica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"4. Enfermedades sistémicas: Diabetes, tirotoxicosis, hipoparatiroidismo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"176","text":"5. Abuso de alcohol.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"176","text":"6. Dieta: Cafeína, bebidas energéticas, lactosa en intolerantes, exceso de FODMAPs.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"176","text":"7. Fármacos: IECA, magnesio, gliptinas, antibióticos, antidepresivos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"176","text":"8. Viajes: Infecciones, parasitosis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"176","text":"9. Uso reciente de antibióticos: Infección por Clostridioides difficile.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"176","text":"10. Baja de peso, anemia, dolor o déficits nutricionales: Enfermedad celíaca, EII.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"175","text":"Clasificación de la\\NDiarrea Crónica","guid":"EhkJIiw_9UgN1uGFO-4v1A","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Acuosa:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• Osmótica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Cede con el ayuno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"• No causa deshidratación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"• Anion gap aumentado, pH ácido <6.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"189","text":"• Investigaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• Prueba de alcalinización de heces.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Test de aliento con lactosa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"• Ac. antitransglutaminasa, biopsia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"193","text":"• Parasitológico, PCR para Giardia.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"188","text":"• Secretora:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• No cede con el ayuno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"• Puede llevar a deshidratación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"• Anion gap normal, pH neutro >6.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"• Investigaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"• VIH, parásitos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"• Medicamentos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"• Secretagogos endógenos (gastrina, cromogranina, 5-HIAA).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"• Colonoscopía + biopsia para colitis colágena, adenoma velloso.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"187","text":"• Esteatorreica\\N(malabsortiva):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Malabsorción\\Nintestinal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"• Inflamatorias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"• Enfermedad celíaca (anticuerpos, biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"• Enf. de Crohn (TAC, endoscopía, biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"209","text":"• Enteritis actínica (historia, endoscopía).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"208","text":"• Infecciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"• Giardia lamblia, Cryptosporidium.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"• Mycobacterium (TBC, avium).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"• Tropheryma whipplei (Enf. de Whipple).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"208","text":"• Infiltrativas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"• Amiloidosis, esclerodermia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"• Linfoma (perdedora de proteínas).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"208","text":"• Anatómica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"• Resección intestinal, by-pass.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"207","text":"• Maldigestión\\Npancreática:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"• Pancreatitis crónica (TAC, grasa fecal, elastasa-1 fecal).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"• Test: Sudán III fecal.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"187","text":"• Disentérica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"• Enfermedad Inflamatoria Intestinal (EII):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"• Colitis ulcerosa (colonoscopía, biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"• Enfermedad de Crohn (TAC, colonoscopía, biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"225","text":"• Colitis actínica (historia, colonoscopía).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"225","text":"• Colitis isquémica (angiografía mesentérica, colonoscopía, biopsia).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"175","text":"• Diarrea intestinal\\Nvs. colónica:","guid":"","child